================================
=  README for ex3: Retirement  =
================================
	


==================
=  Description:  =
==================

The function calculate the pension in given amount of year with constant rate (task 1)
or variable rates (task 2).
Also it can find the best fund for your pension.(task 3)
In task 4 you can check the growth rate in a spesific year(4.1) or update the list of 
the growth rates after the market inflation(4.2).
In the last task(5) you can calculate your retirement saving after your yearly withdraw.




